<i>noun</i>: 협의 [혀븨/혀비], 자문 [자ː문], 숙의 [수긔/수기], 상담 [상담], 배알 [배ː알] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>협의 [혀븨/혀비]</dt><br>
<dd>consultation; discussion</dd><br>
<dd>여러 사람이 모여 서로 의논함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of a group of people sharing opinions with each other.</dd><br>
<dt>자문 [자ː문]</dt><br>
<dd>request for advice; consultation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 더 효율적이고 바르게 처리하기 위해 전문가나 전문 기관에 의견을 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of seeking the opinion of an expert or a professional organization in order to deal with a matter more efficiently.</dd><br>
<dt>숙의 [수긔/수기]</dt><br>
<dd>deliberation; consultation</dd><br>
<dd>깊이 생각하여 충분히 의견을 나눔.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of considering carefully and discussing thoroughly.</dd><br>
<dt>상담 [상담]</dt><br>
<dd>consultation; counseling</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 문제를 해결하기 위하여 서로 이야기함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of talking to one another to solve a certain problem.</dd><br>
<dt>배알 [배ː알]</dt><br>
<dd>audience; consultation; interview</dd><br>
<dd>지위가 높은 사람을 찾아가 만남.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of visiting and meeting a higher-ranking person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>